 "description": "This quiz assesses JavaScript proficiency by testing knowledge of language features spanning ES2015 to ES2022 through multiple‑choice questions. It is positioned at an intermediate difficulty, offering a casual, encouraging tone that emphasizes self‑assessment without requiring registration. The format is concise and playful, aiming to quickly gauge a developer's grasp of modern JavaScript syntax and capabilities.",
